@startuml

title WallRunner v3.0 — 游戏阶段状态图

[*] --> Menu : 启动应用
Menu --> Playing : 玩家点击开始
Playing --> Paused : 按ESC/P暂停
Paused --> Playing : 按ESC/P恢复
Playing --> GameOver : 所有玩家死亡
GameOver --> Menu : 返回主菜单
GameOver --> Playing : 重新开始
Menu --> [*] : 退出应用

state Playing {
    [*] --> Normal
    Normal --> DifficultyUp : 高度达到阈值
    DifficultyUp --> Normal : 难度已提升
    Normal --> CollectibleSpawn : 生成收集物
    CollectibleSpawn --> Normal : 收集物已生成
}

state GameOver {
    [*] --> ShowLeaderboard
    ShowLeaderboard --> WaitRestart : 显示排行榜
    WaitRestart --> [*] : 玩家选择
}

note right of Playing
  内部子状态：
  - Normal: 正常游戏
  - DifficultyUp: 难度递增
  - CollectibleSpawn: 收集物生成
end note
@enduml
